Package hu.klenium.tetris.logic.tetromino

Classes related to the tetromino.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Tetromino
    A shape in Tetris game, which can be controlled by the player.
    TetrominoData
    Helper data structure that stores all informations of a tetromino's parts in a specificed rotation.
    TetrominoDataFactory
    Constructs data for tetrominoes.
